File:王墓山古墳 (倉敷市) 出土 鐘形杏葉.JPG|Bell-shaped horse gear<br>{{small|Tokyo National Museum}}
File:王墓山古墳 (倉敷市) 広口壺 (J-7646).JPG|Sue pottery jar<br>{{small|Tokyo National Museum}}
File:王墓山古墳 (倉敷市) 出土 須恵器 蓋付・須恵器 高台付椀.JPG|Sue pottery lidded vessels and high-footed bowls<br>{{small|Tokyo National Museum}}
</gallery>

